cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically fiducial marker detection algorithms. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The use of color and grayscale also suggests that cs.GR (Graphics) may be relevant. Additionally, the paper discusses experiments and accuracy, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
